org.sbml.squeezer.io
Class SBMLio

java.lang.Object
  org.sbml.squeezer.io.SBMLio
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventListener, ChangeListener, org.sbml.jsbml.SBaseChangedListener, org.sbml.jsbml.SBMLReader, org.sbml.jsbml.SBMLWriter
public class SBMLio
extends Object
implements org.sbml.jsbml.SBMLReader, org.sbml.jsbml.SBMLWriter, org.sbml.jsbml.SBaseChangedListener, ChangeListener

A manager class for reading and writing models from some source into JSBML data objects and to synchronize the model with the original data structure afterwards. This class requires an instance of the so called SBMLReader and SBMLWriter classes and maintains all loaded original model objects and the JSBML representation of it in designated lists. It can be used to, e.g., load a model from CellDesigner's plug-in data structures and save changes back in CellDesigner or to do the same with models that originate from libSBML.

Since:
1.3
Author:
Andreas Dräger andreas.draeger@uni-tuebingen.de
